      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, so it\u2019s spotless inside and out and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for that perfect 'new car' vibe but want to save a bit of cash, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 46500.0,
