    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera 4S represents a masterclass in naturally aspirated performance. At its heart is the M96/03 3.6L flat-six engine featuring VarioCam Plus, delivering a seamless torque curve and visceral induction note. The G96 six-speed manual transaxle provides tactile, short-throw shifts, paired with a viscous-coupling all-wheel-drive system for unparalleled mechanical grip. This example is in peerless mechanical condition, featuring a documented dual-row IMS bearing retrofit and a recently replaced rear main seal. The suspension maintains factory-spec kinematics with refreshed bushings and dampers, ensuring the chassis remains composed under high lateral G-loads. With a flawless undercarriage and an engine bay free of any weeping or seepage, this is a turn-key specimen for the serious driver who demands a factory-fresh tactile experience.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
