    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, preserving its flawless factory paint and deep showroom shine. Inside, the premium leather interior remains supple and completely free of wear, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, functions perfectly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history and exceptionally low mileage that ensures a smooth, powerful, and whisper-quiet driving experience. This is a rare opportunity to own a pristine, turn-key example that requires absolutely nothing. No scratches, no dings, and no compromises.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
